display="inline"><![CDATA[0]]></fr:tex>. In particular, we have:</fr:p><fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[
 \begin {aligned}
   \mathbf {0} &\in  \mathrm {Mat}_{S}{\mathopen {}\left (m,n\right )\mathclose {}}\\
   \mathbf {0}_{i,j} &= 0
 \end {aligned}
]]></fr:tex></fr:mainmatter></fr:tree><fr:tree
