type="local">relations</fr:link></fr:title><fr:taxon>Lemma</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>The pointwise sum <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[M+N]]></fr:tex> of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[M,N\in \mathrm {Mat}_{\mathbb {B}}{\mathopen {}\left (m,n\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> corresponds to the union of the <fr:link
href="jms-00IZ.xml"
title="The relation associated to a matrix"
addr="jms-00IZ"
type="local">relations associated</fr:link> to <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[M]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[N]]></fr:tex>:</fr:p><fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[
 \operatorname {\underline {rel}}_{\mathbb {B}}{\mathopen {}\left (M+N\right )\mathclose {}} =
 \operatorname {\underline {rel}}_{\mathbb {B}}M \cup  \operatorname {\underline {rel}}_{\mathbb {B}}N
]]></fr:tex><fr:p>Moreover, the <fr:link
href="jms-00JP.xml"
title="The zero matrix"
addr="jms-00JP"
type="local">zero matrix</fr:link> corresponds to the <fr:link
href="jms-00IG.xml"
title="The empty relation"
addr="jms-00IG"
type="local">empty relation</fr:link>: <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {\underline {rel}}_{\mathbb {B}}\mathbf {0} = \varnothing ]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
